💭 String Operations Demo
💭 Demonstrates all 5 string ops: STRLEN, SUBSTR, STRINDEX, STR2NUM, NUM2STR

📜 🏠

💭 ── STRLEN ──
💬 "Length of 'hello': "
📢
💬 "hello"
🧵
🖨️

💭 ── SUBSTR ──
💬 "Substr 'hello world'[6:6+5]: "
📢
💬 "hello world"
📥 6
📥 5
✂️
🖨️

💭 ── STRINDEX ──
💬 "Index of 'world' in 'hello world': "
📢
💬 "hello world"
💬 "world"
🔍
🖨️

💭 ── STR2NUM ──
💬 "Parse '42' + 8 = "
📢
💬 "42"
🔁
📥 8
➕
🖨️

💭 ── NUM2STR ──
💬 "Convert 3.14 to string: "
📢
📥 3.14
🔤
🖨️

